    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "Here's how I was able to whip this together pretty quickly, grabbing a comma script from SO. (I'm using `addCommas` elsewhere.)\n\n**HTML**\n\n```\n${{#helpers.addCommas}}{{price}}{{/helpers.addCommas}}\n```\n\n**JavaScript**\n\n```\nsearch.templatesConfig.helpers.addCommas = function(/*text, render*/) {\n   return this.price.toString().addCommas();\n};\n\nString.prototype.addCommas = function() {\n  nStr = this;\n  nStr += '';\n  x = nStr.split('.');\n  x1 = x[0];\n  x2 = x.length > 1 ? '.' + x[1] : '';\n  var rgx = /(\\d+)(\\d{3})/;\n  while (rgx.test(x1)) {\n          x1 = x1.replace(rgx, '$1' + ',' + '$2');\n  }\n  return x1 + x2;\n}\n```\n",
    "created_at": "2016-05-25T20:21:54Z",
